data.description: Don't miss on the opportunity to own this great home! This home is located near St, Johns Parkway in a nice and quite neighborhood. This home is very well maintained and move in ready. This is a 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Some beautiful features of the home is the fireplace in the living room and a large backyard that is ready for you! Call Listing Agent for a showing today!
